bio.singa.structure.model.interfaces

Interface Model

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AtomContainer, ChainContainer, LeafSubstructureContainer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MmtfModel, OakModel

    public interface Model
extends LeafSubstructureContainer, ChainContainer
    Models represent macro molecular structures. Models are most often grouped in Structures where they are different dynamic states of the same molecule.
